ican-the-short-n-sweet-tour-3767338">宣布她的 2024 年北美“The Short N&#39; Sweet 巡演”将于今年晚些时候开始</a>。</p><p>在其他地方，Megan Thee Stallion <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/megan-thee-stallion-seemingly-addresses-fake-ass-a-i-sex-tape-3764093">最近似乎对人工智能生成的使用她肖像的性爱录像做出了回应。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tyler-the-creator-pulls-out-of-lollapalooza-and-outside-lands-replaced-by-megan-thee-stallion-and-sabrina-carpenter-3767350">泰勒，造物主从《Lollapalooza》和《Outside Lands》中撤出，由梅根·西·斯塔林 (Megan Thee Stallion) 和萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 取代，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
